view.name: Metered motorcycle spaces
view.description: This dataset includes metered motorcycle parking spaces in San Francisco as of April 2013. Find attached a data dictionary, a version of the map as a PDF, and a shapefile of the data. This data provides locations of motorcycle meters; meter characteristics, such as single-space or multi-space meter, smart meter status, sensor status, owner, on- or off-street location; rate area.
